content.rendered: Team TTE got together for Iftar on a dhow cruise at Dubai Harbour Marinas earlier this week. Pleasant weather, a beautiful sunset and the illuminated skyline of the Dubai Marina, made it a memorable experience for all. A Tanoura dance performance and puppet show were the other highlights of the evening.
